service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    createNode:
      path: /node
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: Node
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: Node
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              value: value
    createAuthor:
      path: /author
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: Author
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: Author
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              name: name
              books:
                - id: id
                  title: title
    createTree:
      path: /tree
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: TreeNode
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: TreeNode
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              value: value
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  Node:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      value: optional<string>
      next: optional<Node>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Author:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      name: optional<string>
      books: optional<list<Book>>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Book:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      title: optional<string>
      author: optional<Author>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  TreeNode:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      value: optional<string>
      parent: optional<TreeNode>
      children: optional<list<TreeNode>>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Level1:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      level2: optional<Level2>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Level2:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      level3: optional<Level3>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Level3:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      level4: optional<Level4>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Level4:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      level5: optional<Level5>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Level5:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      value: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  BaseEntity:
    properties:
      id: optional<string>
      createdAt: optional<datetime>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Category:
    properties:
      name: optional<string>
      parent: optional<Category>
      subcategories: optional<list<Category>>
    extends:
      - BaseEntity
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
